      <div class="about-intro__content">
        <div class="about-intro__text">
          <p data-i18n="about_company_paragraph_1">Montech Serwis was established in Gdańsk in 2001. The company was founded on extensive experience in shipbuilding and ship repair, as well as knowledge gained in the oil and gas sector.</p>
          <p data-i18n="about_company_paragraph_2">Over the years, we have completed projects for the industrial and marine sectors, working with recognised companies and delivering both new installations and modernisation and maintenance works.</p>
          <p data-i18n="about_company_paragraph_3">Our workshop facilities and qualified team allow us to carry out projects from preparation and prefabrication through to installation at the customer's facility or on board a vessel.</p>
          <p data-i18n="about_company_paragraph_4">We adapt the scope and organisation of our work to the technical requirements and conditions of each project. Our priority is reliable execution, effective cooperation and selecting solutions suited to the customer's needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </section>

